l and Institutional Economics</em>, and <em>Econometrica</em>. His current =
projects include "Generalized Utilitarianism and Harsanyi's Impartial Obser=
ver Theorem" and "Mean-Dispersion Preferences."</p> <p></p></div></div>  </=
